Package: hicdraw
Type: Package
Title: Drawing and Handling of Hi-C Contact Maps and Domain Boundaries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hideki", "Noma", email = "rafysta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for reading, slicing and plotting Hi-C contact maps together
    with boundary-strength and domain annotation tracks. Supports the sparse
    genome-wide bin matrix produced by hic200-cpp as well as the .hic format
    read through 'strawr'. A configuration-file driven interface lets the user
    generate many figures in a single call.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
